title: 199 - It’s a car, IT’S A PLANE!
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a full hause of characters discussing a question posed by Connor, What is your favorite flat soda? With the rather candid start The boys then jump into the POD Fod, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s FOD includes latest updates on television series Ozark and the Yellowstone spin off 1883, The Rock’s new video game project, the car plane, Elon Musk’s latest attempt to turn us into aliens, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
